data.description: Ranch with an amazing layout and convenient location is ready for new owners! Flat, level, fenced-in backyard with deck is perfect for Fall evenings! The striking curb appeal, vaulted ceilings in living room and fireplace are just a few of the features this home has to offer!! With stainless steel appliances, a pass through opening over the sink and cabinets surrounding the fridge this kitchen is ideal for preparing meals and interacting with guests. Large primary bedroom with dual sinks, walk-in closet and separate tub and shower!  Vacant and easy to show, make an appointment to see this one now!!
